headline: Nvidia’s $1 trillion rally has traders primed to ramp back up

headline: Billionaire Bill Ackman Is Loading Up on Uber Technologies Stock. Should You?
summary: Ackman's hedge fund bought 30.3 million shares of Uber in Q1.  Uber could have multiple growth opportunities, but it also faces major uncertainties because of increasing competition.  Bill Ackman is highly selective about which stocks he buys.
